title: FRAM Fresh Breeze Cabin Air Filter Replacement for Car Passenger Compartment w/Arm and Hammer Baking Soda, Easy Install, CF10285 for Toyota Vehicles, white
description: FRAM Fresh Breeze cabin air filter is the only cabin air filter that uses the natural deodorizing properties of ARM & HAMMER embedded in the filter to get rid of odor flowing through the ventilation system. Particles that enter the vehicle with outside air through the vehicle’s air conditioning, heating system and ventilation system can become concentrated and expose passengers to road dust, dirt and particles at higher levels than outside the car. Breathe in cleaner air with a FRAM Fresh Breeze Cabin Air Filter.
